text: Ylitornio () is a municipality in Lapland, Finland. As of 31 December 2020, the municipality had a population of 3,890. Neighbouring municipalities are Pello, Rovaniemi, Tervola and Tornio. Bordering Ylitornio in Sweden is Övertorneå. == Other websites == * Community website Category:Municipalities of Lapland (Finland)
